         <abstract id="aspace_5195008f896af9dd1f6e009b166ed342">The records consist of minutes, correspondence, budgets, manuals, memoranda, and handbooks of the Yale Human Resouces Office. The records document personnel, committees, expenses, and labor unions.</abstract>
